          <text>
            <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Supreme Court Transparency Act </strong></p> <p>This bill requires online publication of ethics reports, personal finance reports, and other disclosure reports regarding the Justices of the Supreme Court. </p> <p>The bill also requires the Justices of the Supreme Court to file periodic transaction reports regarding the purchase, sale, or exchange of stocks, bonds, commodities futures, and other forms of securities when the amount of the transaction exceeds $1,000. </p>]]>
          </text>
